# Personal Profile Website

## Description
This project is an improved version of my Midterm Activity 1 Personal Profile. It is a responsive portfolio website that showcases my background, skills, education, projects, and contact information.

## Features
- Responsive design
- Smooth scrolling
- Contact form integrated with Firebase Firestore
- Hosted on GitHub Pages
- Modern user interface

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Firebase Firestore
- Git & GitHub
- GitHub Pages

## Tools Used
- Visual Studio Code
- Git
- Firebase
- Canva/Figma (if you used either)
- ChatGPT (AI assistant)

